% ---- Final section — climax and cadence (mm.25-29) ----
% Full 8-voice: suspension at cadence, S1 climbs to g'
%
[V:1]  G G F !fermata!E | !sintro!e2 B2 | c2 B2 | A G F2 | E4 !eintro!|]
[V:2]  E E D B, | c2 G2 | G2 G2 | F E D2 | B,4 |]
[V:3]  B, B, G G | G2 E2 | E2 E2 | C D B,2 | G,4 |]
